python backed with fastapi and basic file based db
svelte frontned with shacn-svelte comp lib
docker compose everything together

[main func]
make list to query ytb videos
download the videos
get the most wathced sections of video and cut and edit them
get the narration from audio of the sections {whisper ai}
add subtitles to the screen based on the narration and time it correctly
export the shorts
upload the shorts to ytb or ... based on the settings daily/hourly...
repeat from queue